Docker Publish DinD (linux/amd64)	UNKNOWN STEP	2026-05-02T21:53:11.8627773Z               "message": "test(token-leak): add issue #1745 regression test and update mask-prefix expectations\n\n* tests/test-token-leak-issue-1745.mjs — reproduces the leak shape from\n  xlab2016/space_db_private#20 (env output containing TELEGRAM_BOT_TOKEN\n  embedded in a tool-result comment body) and verifies sanitizeCommentBody\n  strips it. Also exercises containsKnownToken, getEnvironmentTokens,\n  getAllKnownLocalTokens, the leak-notifier contract, and the masked\n  output of formatTokenList.\n\n* tests/test-token-sanitization.mjs — update assertions that were tied\n  to the old 5-char prefix/suffix (e.g. 'ghp_1', 'gho_a', 'AIzaS', 'AKIAI')\n  to the new 3-char default ('ghp', 'gho', 'AIz', 'AKI'). Issue #1745\n  requirement: \"keep only first 3 and last 3 characters\".\n\nThe new test joins the default suite via the @hive-mind-test-suite marker.",
