Docker Publish (linux/arm64)	UNKNOWN STEP	2026-05-02T21:52:36.5465355Z               "message": "docs(case-study): add issue-1745 telegram bot token leak analysis\n\nDocument the leak from xlab2016/space_db_private#20: TELEGRAM_BOT_TOKEN\nended up in a public PR comment because interactive-mode.lib.mjs posted\nraw Bash tool output without running it through sanitizeLogContent.\n\nIncludes timeline, root cause, fix plan, and raw artifacts.",
